      • setClickToEditRowReadOnly

        public void setClickToEditRowReadOnly()
        Sets the internal read only attribute to true on a clicktoedit table. If the table is PPR'd after invoking this API, the active row will be rendered as read only, making the table a read only table.

      • setClickToEditRowEditable

        public void setClickToEditRowEditable()
        Sets the internal read only attribute to false on a clicktoedit table. When the table is PPR'd after invoking this API, the active row will be rendered as editable. Please also see API setClickToEditRowReadOnly. This API is useful to turn the table back to editable after you invoke setClickToEditRowReadOnly.
